    "body": "Good question, that part of the docs is a bit misleading. We actually fork the latest block minus [some value](https://github.com/NomicFoundation/hardhat/blob/421898ea284ef323bc0d9d00c73d0c750051b810/packages/hardhat-core/src/internal/hardhat-network/provider/utils/reorgs-protection.ts#L8) (that depends on the network) to avoid reorg issues.\r\n\r\nDo you think that sentence would be more accurate if it said something like \"Hardhat Network will by default fork from a recent mainnet block\"?",
